{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017qs5N1yuBar1C35paNj3PF","type":"tool_result","content":"A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running an older minor version.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.0 with a controlled rolling update.\n\nRequirements:\n- Keep the cluster available during the upgrade.\n- Ensure the rollout fully completes.\n\nUseful commands:\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n```\n\nVerification:\n1. All pods running new version:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}: {.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n   (All should show v24.1.0)\n\n2. StatefulSet uses new image:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.template.spec.containers[0].image}'\n   (Should be cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0)\n\n3. Verify version via SQL:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT version();\"\n   (Should show v24.1.0)\n\n4. All pods ready:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\n   (All 3 pods should be Running and Ready 1/1)\n\n5. Cluster health:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach node status --insecure\n   (All 3 nodes should be healthy)\n\n6. No partition set:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n   (Should be 0 or empty)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c3c61526-7b33-4cd2-baaa-ead29e48be35","uuid":"94d0edc0-5203-4f0f-a539-e634a8cf8f7c","timestamp":"2026-06-25T14:33:00.822Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running an older minor version.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.0 with a controlled rolling update.\n\nRequirements:\n- Keep the cluster available during the upgrade.\n- Ensure the rollout fully completes.\n\nUseful commands:\n``